I"&<h1 id="system-administration-guide">System Administration guide</h1>

<p>Welcome to the OpenProject <strong>System Administration guide</strong>.</p>

<p>In order to make changes to settings affecting your entire OpenProject environment, you need to navigate to the OpenProject administration.</p>

<p>If you are an administrator on your OpenProject environment,  you can access the administration by clicking on your user Avatar in the upper right corner and selecting -&gt;<em>Administration</em> from the dropdown menu.</p>

<p>Click on one of the categories in order to proceed with the configuration.</p>

<p><img src="image-20201006154046435.png" alt="image-20201006154046435" /></p>

